title: Symmetrical language/environment in SET handlers
summary: Fixed dead code warnings by implementing language/environment suffix building in SET operations to match GET behavior. Added build_storage_key() helper function.

title: Process log format migration to YYMMDD-PXX
summary: Migrated process log format from P001 to date-based YYMMDD-PXX format. Removed redundant date column from INDEX.csv. Updated all documentation and examples.

title: Wire API routes to HttpServer - fix critical dead_code
files_affected: http_server.rs, batch_handlers.rs, REED-07-01 ticket, TICKET-STATUS.md, REED-07-03 ticket
summary: Discovered entire API layer (GET/SET/LIST/BATCH) disconnected from HttpServer causing all API dead_code warnings. Fixed by wiring configure_api_routes() into configure_routes(). Resolved 9 batch_handlers warnings and all other API handler warnings. Created REED-07-03 for missing test coverage (0% handlers).

title: Taxonomy hierarchy.rs warnings - incomplete CLI features
summary: Investigated 9 dead_code warnings in taxonomy/hierarchy.rs. Found REED-04-06 (CLI Taxonomy Commands) marked Complete but acceptance criteria unchecked. Hierarchy functions (get_tree, get_children, etc.) are PUBLIC API but --tree and other CLI features never implemented. Need user decision: suppress warnings vs implement features vs update ticket status.

title: Update tracking files with REED-18/19 tickets
summary: Added 22 new tickets (REED-18-00 through REED-18-07 for ReedCLI, REED-19-00 through REED-19-13 for ReedBase) to tracking system. Updated ticket counts from 54 to 76 tickets. Created Layer 18 and Layer 19 sections in TICKET-STATUS.md. All tickets marked as Planned status for 3-tier architecture restructuring.
